{"title":"Deficit Tiamina Paciente Critico","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/UCI-Medicina Crítica/Deficit Tiamina Paciente Critico.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Déficit de Tiamina en\\Nel Paciente Crítico","guid":"9cBMve6xTNeaToEfXEwT8g","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Bioquímica\\Ny Fisiología","guid":"fpZRsx0AQA66dk-weL_sWg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Vitamina B1 → hidrosoluble, NO sintetizable por humanos","guid":"nGJSKm8QR1efPfR-nuCoAw","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Reservas corporales totales → ~30 mg","guid":"QoQlWQ4TStacSVtnzCFkwQ","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Depleción en ~18 días sin aporte","guid":"0uc-zHVvSUOKv8sIsHJ7Jw","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Forma activa → pirofosfato de tiamina (TPP)","guid":"2jPauC3kSdaM0GJ6DbNBtA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Enzimas\\Ndependientes\\Nde TPP","guid":"LPHyZ47xQmWq4M3RnUJuLg","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"Piruvato deshidrogenasa (PDH) → piruvato → acetil-CoA","guid":"CdTTzY54SFmeNXnZ40KsLg","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"Alfa-cetoglutarato deshidrogenasa → ciclo de Krebs","guid":"GYL1S91oSqq19F_c9_Idxg","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"Transcetolasa → vía de las pentosas fosfato → NADPH","guid":"U6TOdTcySoaZ96w1CMsS9A","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"6","text":"Deshidrogenasa de aminoácidos ramificados","guid":"a4k7-y9_RRG5q4A08k3KKQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"1","text":"Déficit TPP → desvío\\Na metabolismo\\Nanaeróbico","guid":"zrykbjkzRY2OCOu12WyOGQ","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Piruvato → lactato (en vez de acetil-CoA)","guid":"uKYU6a13SPm8YErYQRsqGA","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"ACIDOSIS LÁCTICA TIPO B → sin hipoperfusión","guid":"ts6jP6KhSriJ2ve00Go95Q","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"↓ producción ATP → falla energética celular","guid":"3rNJ