9","parent":"44","text":"Forma incompleta → MÁS\\NFRECUENTE en UCI","guid":"OzlLTHJVQo6Y1yQZH9CI2w","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"Delirium aislado sin signos oculares ni ataxia","guid":"zNOubwNjRq2pT1mjhfMMUQ","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"Confundido con delirium multifactorial / psicosis de UCI","guid":"dME9kxnIRhOnYDwGVxG4gg","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"44","text":"RM cerebral → lesiones periventriculares, cuerpos mamilares","guid":"PKgLbQYkTWCL5cujzI4pTA","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"44","text":"Sin tratamiento → muerte 20% / Korsakoff 85% sobrevivientes","guid":"_YRu3uZwRyiBbLOmrllG_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"43","text":"Beriberi húmedo\\N(cardiovascular)","guid":"EswOZk5BSD6GeJ688x7zAA","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Insuficiencia cardíaca de alto gasto","guid":"or0tRiSpQJK3GIZrYbrRcw","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"Vasodilatación periférica","guid":"CW7YVamOTtOVVa8yFvGY_Q","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"Edema","guid":"Oi0k4_33TyWkn2CLMuIjUw","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"54","text":"Taquicardia","guid":"bdItVbZuRJa6vRhoWu59iA","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"54","text":"RESPUESTA DRAMÁTICA a tiamina EV","guid":"y3xFHR9vT9mwQU0Ig69vbg","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"43","text":"Beriberi seco\\N(neurológico)","guid":"QFwqLF7uSFeOtRvWtecNMQ","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"Polineuropatía sensitivo-motora","guid":"YfO7dZQ2QVWdpq9AIxRpLQ","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"Predominio MMII","guid":"ZQ48GIA2Ta2bGHG3OgRVvg","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"Contribuye a neuropatía del paciente crítico (ICUAW)","guid":"VdvkVA8XSJOqcsYlhmWbZQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"43","text":"Beriberi\\Ngastrointestinal","guid":"KqSmFzamSwqnuxNSMqyMDw","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"Náuseas, vómitos","guid":"eAlTokOsRAqCIlgXhMAtwQ","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"Dolor abdominal","guid":"kR6_lGstS1GiS6nf0JuLmA","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"Disfunción GI en UCI → considerar déficit","guid":"t5poEhZxS_WIq6zGLeMO8A","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"43","text":"Acidosis\\Nláctica tipo B","guid":"9PpHZWK4Qg6IjYymxwD94Q","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"Lactato elevado SIN hipoperfusión tisular","guid":"Rmh81Be_SRSmrdQ9EiNPEA","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"No responde a fluidos ni vasopresores","guid":"LU_CkLydQ_qyBV2ssaZj_w","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"RESPONDE A TIAMINA EV en horas","guid":"efi41ScuRJq7boiVat1-Dg","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"68","text":"Diagnóstico diferencial clave en hiperlactatemia refractaria","guid":"bGbCaa0CRpiqffFJJNTfWA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"Zd9iVQOTQSG0BMcU84_p-w","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"Clínico → alta sospecha en población de riesgo","guid":"_CwZU4I3T3uGuHyjpRi_Bg","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"Niveles séricos\\Nde tiamina","guid":"4PkmDANPSPSwU2zjJWUX9w","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"No disponibles de rutina en mayoría de hospitales","guid":"lT_OwLAfSw-fWR280kEN0A","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"Resultado demora días → NO esperar para tratar","guid":"kAwJrHnYTlyul96AsxK7ow","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"73","text":"TPP eritrocitario\\N(actividad transcetolasa)","guid":"ni5BGJ7JR8aHhYouwy5y6g","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"Más específico que nivel sérico","guid":"oBEe4XXdQWu9yRRm1F8PRg","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"Rara vez disponible en práctica clínica","guid":"ypp6VMvDSweN9Fl_2arbSw","children":[]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"73","text":"DIAGNÓSTICO ES CLÍNICO + RESPUESTA A TRATAMIENTO","guid":"JcQsm4TrSICUbwUqQ48cpA","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"73","text":"RM cerebral → lesiones características (Wernicke)","guid":"VCvJzwJSR7KxD0r5L7mP0w","children":[]},{"id":"83","