4","text":"Shock séptico","guid":"CvULPxMDSteLn_Fm9I6IrA","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"Tiamina 200 mg EV c/12h × 7 días","guid":"YL-0a4UNTKOqBiX04n3WwQ","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"Meta-análisis → ↓ duración shock (MD -11.4h)","guid":"UznM3QUSR8azi-E9ragP9Q","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"99","text":"↓ lactato (MD -0.34 mmol/L)","guid":"M6kgT7gIT7SskXV_XVLsbQ","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"99","text":"↓ SOFA score (MD -1.29)","guid":"-8qxxhX9T2qPNPem_jT2xQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"99","text":"SIN reducción significativa de mortalidad global","guid":"2cyRJncJRwSXnFR1DDVbsQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"84","text":"Consideraciones de\\Nadministración","guid":"wxgBVX_tSBGwrb96RKY9mA","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"EV directo o diluido en SF 0.9% / SG 5%","guid":"1Hk6Ia8ZRe2QARSuGMYD9w","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"Sin reacciones adversas significativas a dosis altas","guid":"a-xtTtXbRDKBSR_b0529FA","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"Anafilaxia → EXTREMADAMENTE rara (1:1.000.000)","guid":"aElKT2TsSguVotBwDGXMbQ","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"Corregir hipomagnesemia → cofactor para activación de tiamina","guid":"gmOhCYYdTp2oQz4XIe4g3w","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"105","text":"Magnesio + tiamina = combinación SINÉRGICA","guid":"HMNN31nMQdyNOJyKJ3rK8g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"111","parent":"0","text":"Evidencia\\NReciente","guid":"Dsiovj8OSN62NGq6A7Z4Tw","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"Nakanishi 2024 →\\Nmeta-análisis 35 RCTs\\N(3494 pacientes)","guid":"CaWbu4ZDRymVdtXrBNa22g","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"↓ duración shock (MD -11.43h, IC 95% -20.16 a -2.69)","guid":"-NXZ9f73SBKQizKUaAdG4A","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"↓ lactato (MD -0.34 mmol/L, IC 95% -0.63 a -0.05)","guid":"4kdrNPPbT1Woe6EYnwdkgw","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"↓ SOFA (MD -1.29, IC 95% -1.91 a -0.66)","guid":"AMXTRU10TCmxDkniXLobAg","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"Sin diferencia mortalidad (RR 0.89, IC 95% 0.75-1.06)","guid":"KqS5Pb89RGejSDeU53tT8A","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"112","text":"↑ leve estancia UCI (MD 0.40 días)","guid":"yhbOKjZURYeDwGzFEAFaeQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"111","text":"TRPSS (Moskowitz 2023)\\N→ RCT placebo-controlado","guid":"TugOpxZoSJyo3mWkWr6kCw","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"Tiamina para protección renal en shock séptico","guid":"WmYkvp-MTQSU0QG2KDWt3g","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"Sin diferencia significativa en outcomes renales","guid":"MnG328PHRseh1QbZTlx8dA","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"111","text":"Dichtwald 2023 → estudio antes-después","guid":"GYS6bh7wTeKTdWAErwhADQ","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"Tiamina → ↓ incidencia delirium en UCI","guid":"QMZAUje4Re-_ksrnma2MMg","children":[]}]},{"id":"123","parent":"111","text":"Wang 2023 → mejoría microcirculación en shock séptico","guid":"FkGZYB0FQE-kyYAiBUOjSg","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"111","text":"Costa → 71.3% déficit tiamina en shock séptico <72h","guid":"P3vvuxVDTr-ZPJOnbn644A","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\NGeriátricas","guid":"zVUgdVodTOOrN0toonlrPA","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"Mayor prevalencia de déficit → desnutrición, polifarmacia","guid":"6yxEIoYBTz-snwbvc_J6qw","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"Diuréticos crónicos → depleción crónica de tiamina","guid":"DWySN6R0R6qfqcRXsQqaYg","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"Delirium en AM → SIEMPRE considerar déficit de tiamina","guid":"X60otEX_SeSEZlaU9XJfqg","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"125","text":"Síndrome de realimentación → mayor riesgo en AM frágil","guid":"KIt8F4bpRre2L2cAGcvadw","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"125","text":"Interacción → fluorouracilo inhibe metabolismo de tiamina","guid":"sa1JcA5gQiKyV5qU4MqYSw","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"125","text":"Deterioro cognitivo → descartar Wernicke-Korsakoff crónico","guid":"FHGyKyBETO6D50MeDf6c4w","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"125","text":"Dosis profiláctica en TODO AM que ingresa a UCI → 100 mg EV/día","guid":"2IZRfppeTaeOV1I0e4BLog","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClínicas","guid":"SULRCFgVR2espP2S4hfVGg","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"Lactato que NO aclara con fluidos ni DVA → pensar en tiamina","guid":"P__UrCxqSrCN3zgyz7XWBA","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"SIEMPRE dar tiamina ANTES de glucosa/dextrosa EV","guid":"_61hb6HZQXGAJEIOsXS7qg","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"Corrección de hipomagnesemia es ESENCIAL → tiamina refractaria sin Mg","guid":"yVE7D-4KRjqsHI5t8X4qBg","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"133","text":"Delirium en UCI sin causa clara → considerar déficit de tiamina","guid":"uS9ohPp2QdC7PKz5M4wnpQ","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"133","text":"Costo tiamina ~$10 por estancia UCI completa vs ~$17.000 por episodio delirium","guid":"rHPU3SPkR06TOPqgYjPSjg","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"133","text":"Profilaxis en TODO paciente con >1 factor de riesgo → sin contraindicación","guid":"MI7d3ZFtTuKKJ5wMZH74lg","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"133","text":"En shock séptico → tiamina reduce duración del shock aunque no mortalidad","guid":"McjAjo5sR0iZByFMDe3cQg","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"133","text":"Síndrome de realimentación → tiamina es la PRIMERA intervención","guid":"LNRhKzPkRL-Mby6PXHGWNg","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"133","text":"El diagnóstico es CLÍNICO → no esperar niveles séricos para tratar","guid":"4vAhy0KiT1i4Tw4eq9snng","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"133","text":"Triada clásica de Wernicke presente solo en 16-38% → buscar formas incompletas","guid":"c5ww5pINSQqnnRwTvEiveA","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":154,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"spe